&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Please include samples of relevant work that you have done - samples that showcase how you would be a good fit for working on Kiva campaigns.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
